title: Rauda Husid
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Western, Scandinavian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located in a historic building in a small town, this bistro labels the vegan dishes on its menu. Offers a gluten-free vegan nut steak with sauteed organic vegetables and salad; salads and vegetable soup; vegan hummus with bread for all meals; pasta primavera with fresh organic vegetables; vegan ice cream and soy milk for coffee drinks. Has Wi-Fi.
